# Terraform
**/.terraform/
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/crash.log
**/crash.*.log
**/*.tfvars
!**/*.tfvars.example

# Local env files
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Global Claude instructions: kept here as source for the ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md symlink, but not tracked
/.claude/CLAUDE.md

# Neovim plugin lockfile — churns on every :Lazy update
/.config/nvim/lazy-lock.json
